column5: Went out for a few hours to see if we could scare up a few fish on the 12 mile. Needless to say the fish were not cooperative. A handful of smaller perch and one sheepie for the son.   Who said fishing season was over?

you guys should wait until you get home before you start eating the fish there Bruce  what fishin season over?...where did you here the kind of nonsense that says there is a beginning and end to fishing season
I'd be happy with a sheephead right now! Good stuff.

I'm a baaad boy     I just couldn't help myself. One moment i"m just fishing away. Minding my own business. Next thing I know I've got this fish in my mouth and I'm hearing the music of ..... "da dum da dum da dum da dum..." Jaws!
and holy carp ya got Rob out fishin again
Great report and pic bigugli May be the fish did not cooperate but you got out and caught a sheppie a tough day fishing is better than a good day at work  Thanks for sharing Leechman
